<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sales Quotation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .company-detail {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .doc-badge {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #ecfdf5;
            color: #059669;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .meta-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .meta-item {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
        }

        .meta-item .label {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .meta-item .value {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .parties-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .party-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .party-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .party-name {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .party-detail {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .salesperson {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .salesperson strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .items-table thead th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .items-table thead th:nth-child(n+3) {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table tbody td {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .items-table tbody td:nth-child(n+3) {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .items-table tbody td:first-child {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
            width: 36px;
        }

        .totals-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .totals-table {
            width: 300px;
        }

        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #374151;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .total-row.discount {
            color: #059669;
        }

        .total-row.grand {
            background: #111827;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .terms-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .terms-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .terms-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .accept-section {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .accept-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .accept-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .accept-field .label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .accept-field .line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #6ee7b7;
            height: 28px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 11px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div>
            <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="company-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if companyPhone}}<div class="company-detail">Phone: {{companyPhone}}</div>{{/if}}
            {{#if companyEmail}}<div class="company-detail">{{companyEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="doc-badge">
            <div class="doc-title">SALES QUOTE</div>
            <div class="badge">Valid {{#if validityDays}}{{validityDays}}{{else}}30{{/if}} Days</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-row">
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">Quote No.</div>
            <div class="value">{{quoteNumber}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">Date</div>
            <div class="value">{{quoteDate}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">Valid Until</div>
            <div class="value">{{#if validUntil}}{{validUntil}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">Currency</div>
            <div class="value">INR (₹)</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parties-grid">
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">From</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="party-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Quote For</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{clientName}}</div>
            <div class="party-detail">{{{clientAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if clientPhone}}<div class="party-detail">{{clientPhone}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    {{#if salesPerson}}<div class="salesperson"><strong>Sales Representative:</strong> {{salesPerson}}</div>{{/if}}

    <table class="items-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>#</th>
                <th>Product / Service</th>
                <th>Qty</th>
                <th>Unit Price</th>
                <th>Amount</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each items}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{@index}}</td>
                <td>{{this.description}}</td>
                <td style="text-align:right;">{{this.quantity}}</td>
                <td>₹{{this.rate}}</td>
                <td>₹{{this.amount}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="totals-section">
        <div class="totals-table">
            <div class="total-row"><span>Subtotal</span><span>₹{{subtotal}}</span></div>
            {{#if discountAmount}}<div class="total-row discount"><span>Discount</span><span>-₹{{discountAmount}}</span>
            </div>{{/if}}
            {{#if taxAmount}}<div class="total-row"><span>GST ({{#if
                    taxRate}}{{taxRate}}{{else}}18{{/if}}%)</span><span>₹{{taxAmount}}</span></div>{{/if}}
            <div class="total-row grand"><span>Grand Total</span><span>₹{{totalAmount}}</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
        <div class="terms-title">Standard Terms & Conditions</div>
        <ol class="terms-list">
            <li><strong>Validity:</strong> This quotation remains valid and binding for {{#if validityDays}}{{validityDays}}{{else}}30{{/if}} days from the date of issuance.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment terms:</strong> {{#if paymentTerms}}{{paymentTerms}}{{else}}To be settled strictly as per the aforementioned schedule. Standard terms dictate 100% advance execution unless mutually agreed otherwise.{{/if}}</li>
            <li><strong>Fulfillment & Delivery:</strong> {{#if deliveryTerms}}{{deliveryTerms}}{{else}}Estimated delivery within 7-10 business days following order confirmation, subject to inventory availability and operational bandwidth.{{/if}}</li>
            <li><strong>Warranty & Support:</strong> {{#if warrantyTerms}}{{warrantyTerms}}{{else}}Covered comprehensively under the prevailing standard manufacturer's warranty policies.{{/if}}</li>
            <li><strong>Liability & Revisions:</strong> Prices and specifications are subject to review and potential structural changes should the scope of work or market conditions be significantly altered post-acceptance.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="accept-section">
        <div class="accept-title">Authorization & Acceptance</div>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #065f46; margin-bottom: 12px;">By affixing my signature below, I acknowledge that I am duly authorized to accept this formal quotation on behalf of my organization and commit to the outlined terms and conditions.</p>
        <div class="accept-grid">
            <div class="accept-field">
                <div class="label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="accept-field">
                <div class="label">Date of Acceptance</div>
                <div class="line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="accept-field">
                <div class="label">Printed Name & Title</div>
                <div class="line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="accept-field">
                <div class="label">Purchase Order No. (If Applicable)</div>
                <div class="line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>We sincerely appreciate the opportunity to serve your business needs. Should you require any further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact us. <br>&copy; {{companyName}}</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>